section.docs--intro
  .row
    .columns.medium-5
      p.docs--hero--text
        | From containers to stateful services, Habitat provides a consistent way to build and manage your applications.
    .columns.medium-7
      ul.docs--feature--list
        li
          | <b>Habitat</b> centers application configuration, management, and behavior around the application itself, not the infrastructure that the app runs on.
        li
          | This means Habitat can provide automation that can programmatically and declaratively build, run, and manage your application and services, both stateful and stateless.
        li
          | In addition, Habitat can be deployed and run on various infrastructure environments, such as bare metal, VM, containers, and PaaS.

